[EXCERPT:Intro]
**Animation Montages** (or, "Montages", for short) enable a wide variety of animation effects, primarily related to exposing animation controls within [Blueprint Visual Scripting](Engine/Blueprints) or through code. They can also be used to create a wide variety of animation effects, including intelligent loops of animation, logic-based animation switching, and much more.
[/EXCERPT:Intro]

